arbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greta-gerwig">格蕾塔·葛韦格</a>执导的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em></a>电影打破了票房纪录，成为年度最受关注的电影之一。因此，导演的粉丝们已经开始期待她的下一个项目，这是可以理解的。</p><p>改编自热门美泰玩具系列的<em>芭比娃娃</em>于上周五（7 月 21 日）在电影院上映。它与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>《奥本海默》</em></a>在同一天首映，两部电影都受到网上“巴本海默”热议的联合宣传。</p><p>葛韦格执导的<em>《芭比娃娃》</em>上映五天在美国票房收入超过 2 亿美元（1.56 亿英镑），打破了女性导演电影首周末票房最高纪录。这部由玛格特·罗比和瑞恩·高斯林领衔主演的讽刺喜剧全球票房也超过了 5 亿美元（3.89 亿英镑），迎来了自大流行前以来电影业最繁忙的一周。</p><p>现在，随着葛韦格背后<em>《芭比娃娃》</em>在经济和评论上的成功，许多人都会好奇这位导演下一步会做什么。</p><h3>格蕾塔·葛韦格的下一部电影是什么？ </h3><figure id="attachment_3355989" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3355989" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3355989" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet.jpg" alt="葛韦格 (Great Gerwig) 担任 2023 年电影《芭比娃娃》导演" width="2000" height="1275" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-400x255.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-800x510.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-696x444.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-1392x887.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-1068x681.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3355989" class="wp-caption-text">伟大的葛韦格认为执导《芭比娃娃》可能会结束她的职业生涯。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>本月早些时候，据透露葛韦格将为<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-react-greta-gerwig-making-chronicles-narnia-films-netflix-3464260">编剧并导演<em>《纳尼亚传奇》</em>宇宙中的两部电影</a>。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2023/07/10/after-barbie-mattel-is-raiding-its-entire-toy-box"><em>《纽约客》</em></a>导演采访时，证实该项目将标志着 Netflix 开始更大范围地打造该系列电影和电视节目。</p><p> <em>《纳尼亚传奇》</em>是 CS Lewis 创作的七本儿童读物系列，之前曾多次被改编为舞台和银幕，最近的改编是三部迪士尼电影： <em>《狮子》、《女巫与魔衣橱》</em> 、 <em>《凯斯宾王子》</em> 、和<em>黎明踏浪号的航行</em>。</p><p>在出现在<em><a class="body-link product-links css-tjvzc4 ebsw2pb0" href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=127X220&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Finside-total-film%2Fid1477057257%3Fi%3D1000621751538%26at%3D11lDJ%26ct%3D1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com%2Fuk%2Fentertainment%2Fa44625805%2Fgreta-gerwig-narnia-remake%2F&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=%5Butm_source%7C%5Butm_campaign%7C%5Butm_medium%7C%5Bgclid%7C%5Bmsclkid%7C%5Bfbclid%7C%5Brefdomain%7C%5Bcontent_id%7C5b2917c6-7503-4200-a359-85184ecc15a1%5Bcontent_product_id%7C997cc240-a851-4a9b-a3c5-8ce5294fadbf%5Bproduct_retailer_id%7C17ed4dfe-e34f-4064-b179-df34f4fd0ee3%5Blt%7C%5Boptxid%7C%5Boptvid%7C" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/inside-total-film/id1477057257?i=1000621751538&amp;at=11lDJ&amp;ct=1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="Total Film Podcast" data-vars-ga-product-id="997cc240-a851-4a9b-a3c5-8ce5294fadbf" data-href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/inside-total-film/id1477057257?i=1000621751538&amp;at=11lDJ&amp;ct=1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4" data-product-url="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/inside-total-film/id1477057257?i=1000621751538&amp;at=11lDJ&amp;ct=1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4" data-affiliate="true" data-affiliate-url="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=127X220&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Finside-to