 Twitter总部屋顶出现新“X”标志引发官方调查https://www.nme.com/news/twitter-sparks-official-investigation-as-new-x-logo-on-roof-of-headquarters-appears-3474938?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=twitter-sparks-总部屋顶出现官方调查新 x 标志JJ NattrassSat, 29 Jul 2023 10:18:36 +0000 NewsElon MuskTwitter https://www.nme.com/?p=3474938 <p><img width="2000" height="1275" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伊隆·马斯克“X”品牌重塑又遭遇麻烦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-400x255.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-800x510.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-696x444.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-1392x887.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-1068x681.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的 Twitter 品牌重塑面临另一个绊脚石</p><p>推特上的<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/twitter-sparks-official-investigation-as-new-x-logo-on-roof-of-headquarters-appears-3474938">帖子引发了官方调查，因为总部屋顶上的新“X”标志</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1275" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伊隆·马斯克“X”品牌重塑又遭遇麻烦" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-400x255.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-800x510.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-696x444.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-1392x887.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Elon-Musk-X-Rebrand-Snafu-1068x681.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk)</a>将<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/twitter">Twitter</a>更名为“X”的计划本周面临另一个绊脚石，因为这家科技巨头在总部屋顶竖立公司新徽标时被叫停。</p><p>据报道，周五（7 月 28 日）该公司被要求暂停在旧金山总部屋顶建造新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/major-gaming-companies-poke-fun-at-twitters-new-name-x-3472598">“X”标志</a>。据<em><a href="https://deadline.com/2023/07/new-twitter-logo-x-nayd-by-san-francisco-officials-as-its-installed-investigation-underway-1235450799/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deadline</a></em>报道，据说市政府官员已经停止了正在制作的标志，并对该公司的行为展开调查。</p><p>据信该市代表曾表示，这个巨大的“X”标志没有适当的设计和安全许可，无法在屋顶上竖立。 </p><figure id="attachment_3474950" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3474950" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3474950" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Twitter-X-sing-being-built.jpg" alt="Twitter 更名为“X”面临新障碍" width="2000" height="1275" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Twitter-X-sing-being-built.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Twitter-X-sing-being-built-400x255.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Twitter-X-sing-being-built-800x510.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Twitter-X-sing-being-built-696x444.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Twitter-X-sing-being-built-1392x887.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Twitter-X-sing-being-built-1068x681.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3474950" class="wp-caption-text"> Twitter 的“X”标志正在旧金山总部顶部建造（图片来源：Getty）</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2023/jul/28/x-logo-installed-atop-twitter-building-spurring-sa/?utm_source=RSS_Feed&amp;utm_medium=RSS" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《华盛顿时报》</em></a>率先报道了这一混乱局面，并援引建筑检查部发言人帕特里克·汉南 (Patrick Hannan) 的话说，任何替换字母或符号都需要获得许可，以确保“与建筑物的历史性质保持一致”并遵守规定并采取安全措施。</p><p>汉南周五在接受该刊物采访时补充说，在建筑物顶部竖立标志也需要获得许可。据信，X 没有获得正确的许可来遵守有关新标志及其在建筑物上的位置的城市章程。</p><p>屋顶标志并不是马斯克<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-hints-that-twitter-is-to-imminently-rebrand-as-x-3472179">上周出人意料地重新命名 Twitter</a>后面临的第一个障碍。本周早些时候，市政府官员介入，阻止拆除大楼内旧的 Twitter 标志（一只巨大的蓝鸟）。该市声称这是因为工人们没有用胶带封住人行道，以确保在施工期间万一有东西掉落时行人的安全。</p><p>推特上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/twitter-sparks-official-investigation-as-new-x-logo-on-roof-of-headquarters-appears-3474938">的帖子引发了官方调查，因为总部屋顶上的新“X”标志</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
